Package: mieitesti
Title: Italian News Article Collection and Text Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Giampaolo", "Montaletti",
           email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122"))
Description: Tools for collecting and analyzing Italian news articles from
    'il sussidiario' and ISTAT RSS feeds. Provides functions for web scraping,
    text parsing, and includes Italian stopwords for text analysis.
